description:
After finding a midi recreation source, I've redone everything from scratch. It was absolutely worth it. 

Changes:
 - Changed the guitars to synths
 - Completed the drum track
 - Revamped the main lead
 - Added the background track
 - Made it all accurate with no undercharted sections
 - Made a dedicated track for Xyphos (as it's 9 octaves)
 - Much more.
title: Soulless 5
